panels.title: aggregation events sent grouped by type and name

targets.query: SELECT mean("featureBucketAggrMetadaSaves") AS "aggregation metadatas created", mean("sentToQueue") AS "aggregation metadatas sent to queue" FROM "aggregation.service.aggr-feature-events.bucket-conf" WHERE "confName" =~ /^$bucket_name$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), "confName" fill(null)

SELECT mean("featureBucketAggrMetadaSaves") AS "aggregation metadatas created", mean("sentToQueue") AS "aggregation metadatas sent to queue" FROM "aggregation.service.aggr-feature-events.bucket-conf" WHERE "confName" =~ /^$bucket_name$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), "confName" fill(null)
